---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="section-narrow">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">About</div>
    <h1 class="section-title">Curated weekly.</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>After Hours is a curated listing of live shows in rooms that hold under 1,000 people. Local bands, touring acts that bypass the arenas, DJ nights, album release parties, jazz sessions, basement folk shows.</p>
      <p>The room matters as much as the act. A 240-cap club has a different relationship with the music than a 20,000-seat venue does. This site is for shows where the room is part of the point.</p>
      <p class="muted">Press, venue submissions, and corrections: <span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--secondary)">listings@afterhours.test</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
